{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01LBKa23cA5mZwtRV1hkwNTM","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Audit Module\n     2→\n     3→Compliance audit coordinator. Checks all dimensions (observability, testing, documentation, verification, infrastructure) and reports project health.\n     4→\n     5→## Files\n     6→\n     7→- `types.ts` — DimensionStatus, DimensionResult, AuditGap, AuditResult type definitions\n     8→- `dimensions.ts` — Per-dimension checkers: checkObservability, checkTesting, checkDocumentation, checkVerification, checkInfrastructure\n     9→- `index.ts` — Barrel exports + runAudit coordinator that calls all dimension checkers\n    10→- `report.ts` — formatAuditHuman (UX prefix format) and formatAuditJson (structured output)\n    11→\n    12→## Key Patterns\n    13→\n    14→- Coordinator pattern: runAudit calls 5 dimension checkers, collects results, computes overall status\n    15→- Each dimension checker wraps an existing module function and maps output to DimensionResult\n    16→- Result<T> discriminated union for error handling — never throws\n    17→- Graceful degradation: each checker catches its own errors, returns warn/fail instead of crashing\n    18→- Barrel imports only: consumers import from index.ts\n    19→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01UmDTVZ4iS72Xuw7ncmN4YZ","session_id":"e1f3df9b-d919-466e-880e-1001c8652ee8","uuid":"be00bf7d-9ed7-46a9-9522-bb9ec0ed79df","timestamp":"2026-03-20T08:52:19.405Z"}
